title: NFL Week 8 Fantasy, Gambling Breakdown with Heath Cummings, Kelly Stewart (Football 10/25)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Heath Cummings to break down everything you need to know about Week 8 of the 2018 NFL season from a fantasy perspective. Then Kelly Stewart of SportsLine joins the show to talk about her leans for the Week 8 gambling slate.
